SPH RUN GUID
1) Install OpenGL library 
	sudo apt-get install freeglut3 freeglut3-dev
	sudo apt-get install binutils-gold
2) Istall OpenCL library for your devices, you can find it in site of vendor of your device, this version works fine on Intel processors, on another devices we steel need to test it.

you chould run g++ with this library - OpenCL, rt, glut, GL, GLU


